{"tid":1105671,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"龜頭炎睇咩醫生？","createTime":"2019-04-14T05:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T11:15:47.000Z","uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3c40ef4ca87c881818f278bb620aa3d4765f93a1","tid":1105671,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜日至一開始龜頭有紅點<br />\n好似有少少甩皮 <br />\n過多一兩日包皮有少少紅腫同埋痕<br />\n咁我每日就早晚洗一次 <br />\n過多兩日用埋生理鹽水洗<br />\n而家就淨返包皮少少紅同痕<br />\n斷斷續續成個禮拜都仲有啲啲痕<br />\n上網睇過好多post都應該係龜頭炎<br />\n想問睇左普通診所先定直接睇專科診所好？<br />\n如果係，邊個醫生好啲？<br />\nThx"},{"pid":"684d4fbf39bde817eb02debed7764c48ead0767d","tid":1105671,"uid":146617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"連登醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc41ee09a5fd32b9fb595a42b821c32583eadcbd","tid":1105671,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"耳鼻喉科"},{"pid":"cde3642b4337fcc9635080d0b3df0d8217c1e390","tid":1105671,"uid":201091,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"婦產科"},{"pid":"8a432109b3ca55e9fccae48f49e99a85c2fca197","tid":1105671,"uid":246419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"性病？"},{"pid":"47e34610139f8f36b2aef7600c398d19d7304584","tid":1105671,"uid":206372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"有任何病:<br />\n上連登問問先"},{"pid":"7434d101ea638cc0efaa5fbc0bcf3f6ba29b8872","tid":1105671,"uid":210638,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"獸醫"},{"pid":"15728450b74422aaaf0882a7c35ebd59fe26afc7","tid":1105671,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"無巴打試過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e41b2d12a239fca1ccbbc08ddaec482a50ce09","tid":1105671,"uid":2